{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/03/11/snap添加代理.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2b330349-4989-5f52-8ad3-8bbe5606dd64","excerpt":"为 snap 添加代理 想在腾讯云里面做个 CI，本着用新不用旧的思想，我打算试试搭建 microk8s。可是我国强大的网络环境无法导致无法安装，也没有个大厂出一个镜像解围，只好挂下代理解决。 sslocal 注意，腾讯云里面安装 sslocal 会被和谐的，但是试了下 docker…","html":"<h1>为 snap 添加代理</h1>\n<p>想在腾讯云里面做个 CI，本着用新不用旧的思想，我打算试试搭建 microk8s。可是我国强大的网络环境无法导致无法安装，也没有个大厂出一个镜像解围，只好挂下代理解决。</p>\n<h2>sslocal</h2>\n<p>注意，腾讯云里面安装 sslocal 会被和谐的，但是试了下 docker 却可以，我安装了 <a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/teachmyself/sslocal\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">teachmyself/sslocal</a> ，目前没问题。</p>\n<h2>修改<code class=\"language-text\">/etc/environment</code></h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-ini line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"token constant\">http_proxy</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>http://[服务器地址]:[端口号]</span>\n<span class=\"token constant\">https_proxy</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>http://[服务器地址]:[端口号]</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>重启 snap 即可</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo systemctl restart snapd</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/snap添加代理.html","date":"March 11, 2020","title":"snap添加代理"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/snap添加代理.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/应该是目前最好的WSL2和Virtualbox共存的方法了.html","title":"应该是目前最好的WSL2和Virtualbox共存的方法了"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/使用docker安装Jenkins.html","title":"使用docker安装Jenkins"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}